  "title": "A witness saw a white cigar shaped UFO flying low in Curitiba [2000]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/14/a-witnesse-saw-a-white-cigar-shaped-ufo-flying-low-in-curitiba-2000/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-sa",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JULY 13th, 2000</strong>. Time: 3:20 pm. Duration: 5 minutes. A witness residing in the center of the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná, reported the sighting of an unidentified flying object in the form of a &#8220;cigar&#8221; and white color. The UFO flew at a very low speed and at an altitude of 1km. The object that was sighted under good visibility conditions, moved from North to South without leaving trails of condensation or emitting any audible noise to the witness of the sighting.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.580. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni na cidade de Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
